'''

INSTALLATION : 

    CHECK IF INSTALLED : 
        
        sudo systemctl status postfix

        mailx -V

    INTSALL : 
        
        sudo apt install postfix

        sudo apt install mailutils

    START SERVICE : sudo systemctl start postfix.service


CONFIGURATION : 

    FILE LOCATION :  /etc/postfix/main.cf

    EDIT : sudo vi main.cf

    ADD LINES : 

        relayhost = [smtp.gmail.com]:587 
        myhostname = HostName

        Location of sasl_passwd we saved :

            smtp_sasl_password_maps = hash:/etc/postfix/sasl/sasl_passwd

        Enables SASL authentication for postfix :

            smtp_sasl_auth_enable = yes
            smtp_tls_security_level = encrypt

        Disallow methods that allow anonymous authentication :
            smtp_sasl_security_options = noanonymous
            
    CREATE DIRECTORY AND FILE FOR PASSWORD : 
        
        mkdir /etc/postfix/sasl

        touch /etc/postfix/sasl/sasl_passwd

    ADD LINES IN FILE : 

        [smtp.gmail.com]:587 MyEmailId@gmail.com:password

            PASSWORD GENERATION : 

                manage google account
                ensure 2 step verification
                app passwords
                create new
                copy and paste that password

            MAKE DB FILE OF PASSWORD : 

                postmap sasl_passwd

EMAIL FORMAT : 

    echo "Email body here" | mutt -s "Subject Here" -a /home/ratri0kali/hello.txt -- ratrisubscriber001@gmail.com


'''